<br />

<br />
  I've tried various other forms of anti-spam protection [ are you human, yes or no? radio button ] and some others that didn't seem to function @ registration time [ possibly due to the large combination of anti-spam measures ].  So I just reset all the associated php files, and I'm now using your mod.
<br />

<br />
  It was by far the easiest to install, and I've tested it and all seems well.  Now I can get back to my REAL work LOL.  Not deleting porn spam all day heh.
<br />

<br />
